elements.name: Cancelling a booked hotel after generating order id

steps.name: UserG should click login button and navigated to search hotel page
UserG should select a "Sydney", "Hotel Creek", "Standard", "1 - One", "18/03/2021", "19/03/2021", "2 - Two", "4 - Four"
UserG should click search button and user is on select hotel page, click that radio button and user should click continue button
UserG should select the Booked Itinerary
UserG should select the cancel id button and verify the message

elements.name: Cancelling a booked hotel for existing order id

steps.name: UserH should click login button and navigated to search hotel page
UserH should select the Booked Itinerary
UserH should select the cancel id button and verify the message
